description.displayText: Liz provided our Foundation's Leadership Team with a comprehensive data collection system documenting the organization's significant impact on 4000+ Early Childhood Educators.(1997-2014). Her detailed research and compilation presentation now allows for the acquisition of support and resources necessary for meeting our goal to increase the designation of High Quality Early Childhood Educators throughout the state of Georgia. I highly recommend Liz as an exceptional professional and a committed Team Player.
